WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Support us and become VIP member 
to remove all ads from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:00:44.944 --> 00:00:48.380
Hurry. Get ready to operate.

3
00:00:52.218 --> 00:00:54.209
Hurry up!

4
00:01:02.562 --> 00:01:03.790
It's stillborn.

5
00:01:05.298 --> 00:01:07.698
- Stop the bleeding.
- Wait. one more.

6
00:01:10.036 --> 00:01:11.333
Sponge.

7
00:01:11.538 --> 00:01:13.768
We're losing the mother.
Commence CPR quickly.

8
00:01:14.007 --> 00:01:15.770
Help stop the bleeding.

9
00:01:16.443 --> 00:01:18.604
Hurry. Come help. hurry.

10
00:02:43.663 --> 00:02:48.498
The two guys upstairs raped
the daughter of Judge Chen...

11
00:02:49.536 --> 00:02:52.664
...of the Supreme Court.
What should we do?

12
00:02:56.809 --> 00:02:59.073
Kuo called.

13
00:03:04.117 --> 00:03:05.846
Zhong Xiang said so.

14
00:03:08.087 --> 00:03:09.782
Did you get permission from her?

15
00:03:09.989 --> 00:03:14.824
- She seduced us.
- She did? Was she nuts?

16
00:03:31.544 --> 00:03:33.136
Stop this. That's enough.

17
00:03:34.480 --> 00:03:36.539
Captain. that's enough.

18
00:03:37.984 --> 00:03:39.349
That's enough.

19
00:03:40.453 --> 00:03:42.114
What's with you today?

20
00:03:43.856 --> 00:03:47.314
Take him to the sick room.
Say he tried to commit suicide.

21
00:04:03.309 --> 00:04:06.801
You didn't know her father
works at the Supreme Court?

22
00:04:11.184 --> 00:04:13.015
Do me a favor. okay?

23
00:04:13.186 --> 00:04:16.644
Next time.
settle on a price first. okay?

24
00:04:32.105 --> 00:04:33.436
What are you doing here?

25
00:04:33.806 --> 00:04:35.797
Sleeping at your office again tonight?

26
00:04:36.876 --> 00:04:39.208
Is your office really that comfortable?

27
00:04:39.379 --> 00:04:41.472
It stinks worse than the restroom here.

28
00:04:41.714 --> 00:04:45.172
Every day. you don't go home.
you ignore your wife and child.

29
00:04:45.385 --> 00:04:49.287
Just hole yourself up in your
damn office. playing your damn chess.

30
00:04:50.056 --> 00:04:51.921
Who would feel sorry for you?

31
00:04:52.625 --> 00:04:56.959
Do you look like someone working for
the Foreign Affairs unit?

32
00:05:05.471 --> 00:05:08.269
Damn. how come this won't wash out?

33
00:05:57.390 --> 00:06:00.450
Tai Feng Chemical Group

34
00:07:39.492 --> 00:07:41.392
My brother works for the government.

35
00:07:41.561 --> 00:07:43.461
How long have you worked here?

36
00:07:43.629 --> 00:07:46.655
Miss? Why isn't the air conditioning on?

37
00:07:46.866 --> 00:07:50.097
- Boss told us to turn it off.
- Don't you know how hot it is?

38
00:07:50.303 --> 00:07:54.967
Two hours ago. the boss kept telling me
the office was too cold.

39
00:07:55.141 --> 00:07:59.544
I gave him a blanket.
but still he said it was too cold.

40
00:07:59.745 --> 00:08:02.714
So he told us to turn off
the air conditioning.

41
00:08:02.882 --> 00:08:06.716
You can turn it on now. since your boss
has kicked the bucket.

42
00:08:22.869 --> 00:08:24.803
What is the situation?

43
00:08:25.872 --> 00:08:29.205
Captain. do you know who he is?

44
00:08:30.243 --> 00:08:32.074
The chairman
of the Tai Feng Corporation.

45
00:08:34.347 --> 00:08:36.747
The one who dumped toxic waste...

46
00:08:36.983 --> 00:08:38.211
...into the river?
- Yes.

47
00:08:38.384 --> 00:08:39.078
Come with me.

48
00:08:39.485 --> 00:08:44.081
The medics took one look at him
and called us.

49
00:08:46.926 --> 00:08:51.192
It's ridiculous.
I believe he was drowned...

50
00:08:51.364 --> 00:08:53.594
...in icy water.

51
00:08:53.833 --> 00:08:56.199
The mucus in his
nasal cavities is frozen.

52
00:08:56.502 --> 00:08:57.867
Drowned?

53
00:09:11.450 --> 00:09:14.851
You are with Foreign Affairs.
This is not your case.

54
00:09:15.054 --> 00:09:16.681
What are you doing here?

55
00:09:17.356 --> 00:09:19.051
Might this not be
the original crime scene?

56
00:09:19.225 --> 00:09:24.686
This scene is perfectly intact. And his
employees say he never left his office.

57
00:09:25.197 --> 00:09:28.030
- What case?
- I said. I have a case here.

58
00:09:28.801 --> 00:09:32.862
On such a hot day as today.
the boss of a major corporation...

59
00:09:33.039 --> 00:09:37.066
...drowns in his 17th-floor office.

60
00:09:41.847 --> 00:09:44.577
What the hell are you doing here?

61
00:09:45.685 --> 00:09:47.744
What case are you on?

62
00:09:49.055 --> 00:09:51.523
- What are you doing?
- What is he doing here?

63
00:09:51.724 --> 00:09:52.748
Captain.

64
00:09:54.093 --> 00:09:56.653
Huo-tu. you have no business here.
Go back.

65
00:10:07.473 --> 00:10:09.373
- Espin Pinosa?
- Yes. sir.

66
00:10:09.542 --> 00:10:10.668
I've got to bring you in...

67
00:10:10.876 --> 00:10:14.607
...for violating Taiwan's
labor agreement with the Philippines.

68
00:10:14.814 --> 00:10:16.782
- Understand?
- I don't understand.

69
00:10:17.683 --> 00:10:20.151
I'm arresting you.

70
00:10:20.386 --> 00:10:22.547
No! Why? Why's that?

71
00:10:22.722 --> 00:10:24.155
Why is that? No.

72
00:10:25.891 --> 00:10:26.789
No...

73
00:10:51.917 --> 00:10:53.782
Mei-mei. go outside.

74
00:10:54.387 --> 00:10:56.150
Mommy wants to talk to Daddy.

75
00:10:57.957 --> 00:10:58.821
Mei-mei.

76
00:11:01.360 --> 00:11:02.418
Mei-mei.

77
00:11:09.035 --> 00:11:13.301
- What happened to her neck?
- That was last week's news.

78
00:11:13.873 --> 00:11:17.502
Her classmate shot at her
with a toy gun at naptime.

79
00:11:18.678 --> 00:11:22.273
Didn't I tell you
not to bring Mei-mei here?

80
00:11:27.053 --> 00:11:29.146
When was the last time you came home?

81
00:11:31.157 --> 00:11:32.852
The teacher wants a meeting
with her parents.

82
00:11:33.325 --> 00:11:37.056
I cannot take another day off.
You go this time.

83
00:11:46.138 --> 00:11:48.538
I'll take these clothes home to wash.

84
00:11:55.414 --> 00:11:58.815
I think Mei-mei should stay with you.

85
00:11:59.018 --> 00:12:01.509
It's better for her
to be with her mother.

86
00:12:02.455 --> 00:12:05.288
Why make us miserable too?

87
00:12:07.526 --> 00:12:09.517
Mei-mei. we're going home.

88
00:12:29.548 --> 00:12:31.482
I've never seen anything like it.

89
00:12:32.118 --> 00:12:35.679
His epidermal and dermal layers
were completely frozen.

90
00:12:37.690 --> 00:12:41.148
How is that possible?
Is there water in his lungs?

91
00:12:41.627 --> 00:12:43.288
Not one drop.

92
00:12:43.629 --> 00:12:45.290
But his brain...

93
00:12:46.165 --> 00:12:48.030
Come look at this.

94
00:12:48.868 --> 00:12:53.498
This is the thalamus. Seat of
the nervous system. Guess what that is?

95
00:12:54.440 --> 00:12:55.498
What is it?

96
00:12:57.143 --> 00:13:01.671
- It looks like mold.
- Yes. It is mold bacteria.

97
00:13:03.048 --> 00:13:08.179
This was scraped out of his sinus
cavity. same bacteria as in his brain.

98
00:13:09.522 --> 00:13:11.683
What did you put for cause of death?

99
00:13:16.262 --> 00:13:18.253
"Suspected drowning."

100
00:13:19.832 --> 00:13:22.164
- Is that a good thing to do?
- No.

101
00:13:22.768 --> 00:13:23.700
It's not good at all.

102
00:13:25.771 --> 00:13:28.399
- Is it toxic?
- Don't know.

103
00:13:28.941 --> 00:13:32.672
Taiwan can't find out.
Our technology is too far behind.

104
00:13:35.948 --> 00:13:37.745
Where can we find out?

105
00:13:39.585 --> 00:13:42.713
Quantico. Virginia. U.S.A.

106
00:13:43.122 --> 00:13:46.091
FBI ACADEMY

107
00:13:52.364 --> 00:13:53.661
Anyway...

108
00:13:54.333 --> 00:13:56.062
...the U.S. Is not
only the biggest producer...

109
00:13:56.302 --> 00:13:58.793
...of movies
and nuclear weapons.

110
00:13:59.071 --> 00:14:01.369
We're also number one
in serial killers.

111
00:14:02.541 --> 00:14:04.634
Now. when we give these classes...

112
00:14:05.244 --> 00:14:07.804
...what the bureau doesn't want us
to tell you is that...

113
00:14:09.081 --> 00:14:10.639
...we still fail.

114
00:14:11.917 --> 00:14:14.044
Every rule has its exception...

115
00:14:14.386 --> 00:14:17.753
...and you learn from failure.
So...

116
00:14:19.358 --> 00:14:20.757
...let's start there.

117
00:14:24.063 --> 00:14:27.396
Okay. in 1994.
a total of nine corpses...

118
00:14:27.600 --> 00:14:30.535
...were found
in the suburbs of St. Louis.

119
00:14:30.836 --> 00:14:32.701
All boys...

120
00:14:32.905 --> 00:14:37.035
...all found lying like this:

121
00:14:37.543 --> 00:14:42.446
Posed. facedown.
Cause of death was strangulation.

122
00:14:42.915 --> 00:14:46.749
There were no bruises.
no signs of struggle.

123
00:14:47.219 --> 00:14:49.187
No evidence of molestation either.

124
00:14:49.688 --> 00:14:51.451
All the victims were runaways.

125
00:14:52.057 --> 00:14:54.890
Kids who slipped through the cracks.
et cetera.

126
00:14:56.195 --> 00:14:58.459
I drew up a profile
of the type we call the...

127
00:14:58.564 --> 00:15:02.159
..."preferential offender."
Street predator.

128
00:15:02.635 --> 00:15:05.160
White male. of course.

129
00:15:06.005 --> 00:15:09.497
Loner. Out of work or itinerant.

130
00:15:09.875 --> 00:15:13.367
Socially inept.
sexually repressed. an outcast.

131
00:15:13.579 --> 00:15:15.342
But when the killer
turned himself in...

132
00:15:15.547 --> 00:15:18.380
- He surrendered?
- Yes.

133
00:15:18.651 --> 00:15:21.711
Walked into his local police department.

134
00:15:22.855 --> 00:15:25.153
As if that wasn't embarrassing enough...

135
00:15:25.424 --> 00:15:28.825
...we soon found that except
for the "white male" part...

136
00:15:28.994 --> 00:15:33.863
...he did not correspond
to one single detail of my profile.

137
00:15:35.534 --> 00:15:38.503
In fact. I couldn't have been
any more wrong.

138
00:15:43.976 --> 00:15:45.910
That's not even the strange part.

139
00:15:46.145 --> 00:15:49.205
The strange part were the victims'
expressions.

140
00:15:57.256 --> 00:15:59.281
Are they smiling?

141
00:16:00.392 --> 00:16:02.986
Sure appears that way. doesn't it?

142
00:16:05.965 --> 00:16:09.332
Almost as if they were on
some kind of a high...

143
00:16:09.501 --> 00:16:11.059
...at the moment of their deaths...

144
00:16:12.338 --> 00:16:14.238
...in a state of bliss.

145
00:16:19.178 --> 00:16:23.774
HSIN-YI DISTRICT. TAIPEl

146
00:17:16.769 --> 00:17:20.296
Fire department?
My home is on fire.

147
00:17:22.174 --> 00:17:25.143
I'm at Alley 200. Section 3.
Hsin-yi Road...

148
00:17:35.621 --> 00:17:40.558
SENATOR'S WIFE
TO SUE CHIU FOR ADULTERY

149
00:17:50.302 --> 00:17:52.532
I've never experienced
this kind of situation before.

150
00:17:52.771 --> 00:17:57.174
- Of course I'm scared.
- I am too.

151
00:17:57.810 --> 00:17:59.072
She's the one?

152
00:17:59.578 --> 00:18:02.638
- The senator's mistress?
- She's the one.

153
00:18:02.815 --> 00:18:04.544
Bailed out just this morning.

154
00:18:05.751 --> 00:18:07.241
Who reported this?

155
00:18:08.387 --> 00:18:12.221
She called the fire department
an hour ago to report a fire.

156
00:18:12.458 --> 00:18:15.484
- They hurried over.
- And no sign of a fire at all.

157
00:18:15.794 --> 00:18:16.954
No.

158
00:18:18.997 --> 00:18:22.262
Your face looks worse than hers.

159
00:18:25.604 --> 00:18:26.969
Look at her arms.

160
00:18:28.140 --> 00:18:31.007
This peculiar kind of contortion...

161
00:18:31.276 --> 00:18:33.642
...is caused by severe
muscular dehydration.

162
00:18:33.812 --> 00:18:36.178
This situation only happens to...

163
00:18:36.448 --> 00:18:40.509
...corpses burned to death
at very high temperatures.

164
00:18:41.086 --> 00:18:42.747
But here...

165
00:18:43.288 --> 00:18:44.687
How could it be?

166
00:18:48.927 --> 00:18:50.189
"Suspected murder...

167
00:18:50.462 --> 00:18:51.929
...cause of death unknown"?

168
00:18:52.731 --> 00:18:53.698
This doesn't look good.

169
00:18:53.932 --> 00:18:56.457
My report is based on current evidence.

170
00:18:56.702 --> 00:19:00.035
And I feel both cases are related.

171
00:19:01.406 --> 00:19:05.069
Re-examine the corpse.
Rewrite the report.

172
00:19:06.612 --> 00:19:08.239
As if we don't have
enough problems already.

173
00:19:08.447 --> 00:19:11.905
Getting tangled up in
a politician's personal affairs.

174
00:19:13.986 --> 00:19:15.817
Re-examine her heart.

175
00:19:16.054 --> 00:19:21.219
People die of heart attacks every day!

176
00:19:22.494 --> 00:19:25.554
TEACHERS' OFFICE

177
00:19:25.998 --> 00:19:28.865
This is Su Chao-pin.
He cut your daughter's hair...

178
00:19:29.168 --> 00:19:31.898
...during naptime today.

179
00:19:32.237 --> 00:19:35.798
Then she scratched his eye.

180
00:19:35.974 --> 00:19:37.805
Last week...

181
00:19:38.010 --> 00:19:41.776
This is Huang Chin-feng.
Your daughter fought with him.

182
00:19:42.114 --> 00:19:44.844
Mr. Huang. excuse me...

183
00:19:45.083 --> 00:19:47.142
...I risk offense to ask a question.

184
00:19:47.319 --> 00:19:50.755
I am thinking. would it be better
if you sent her...

185
00:19:51.323 --> 00:19:53.086
...to a special school?

186
00:20:16.248 --> 00:20:18.011
Huang Mei-mei's parent.

187
00:20:19.218 --> 00:20:21.049
Huang Mei-mei's parent.

188
00:20:44.042 --> 00:20:46.101
Has she been taking her medication?

189
00:20:46.912 --> 00:20:50.746
I don't know. I suppose so.

190
00:20:51.049 --> 00:20:52.277
You "suppose"?

191
00:21:27.386 --> 00:21:31.686
She hates taking them.
But I haven't been home recently.

192
00:21:31.923 --> 00:21:35.484
The pills don't work so well.
But she should take them.

193
00:22:54.673 --> 00:22:58.734
CHURCH OF NEW TRUTH. TAMSUI

194
00:23:59.004 --> 00:24:00.198
Hello?

195
00:24:01.840 --> 00:24:02.864
What?

196
00:24:26.331 --> 00:24:29.494
Mei-mei. it's just a dream.

197
00:24:36.475 --> 00:24:38.466
JIAN MING LEGAL SERVICES

198
00:24:42.481 --> 00:24:44.745
DIVORCE AGREEMENT

199
00:25:12.544 --> 00:25:16.207
Father Lorenzo died
in his own room last night.

200
00:25:16.615 --> 00:25:17.775
Murdered.

201
00:25:18.283 --> 00:25:21.411
This case is sensitive
because of his identity.

202
00:25:21.586 --> 00:25:24.214
Taiwan must go through this man
to buy weapons from America.

203
00:25:24.456 --> 00:25:27.254
The foreign press will be here.
you deal with them.

204
00:25:27.459 --> 00:25:30.986
I have left Homicide.
Leave me alone. would you?

205
00:25:31.162 --> 00:25:33.722
Foreign Affairs handles
foreigners in Taiwan.

206
00:25:33.965 --> 00:25:36.559
And you speak the best English.
It's all yours.

207
00:25:41.940 --> 00:25:43.066
What happened?

208
00:25:43.975 --> 00:25:46.842
Time of death. 3 a.m.

209
00:25:47.012 --> 00:25:50.243
There were at least two murderers.

210
00:25:50.916 --> 00:25:55.250
While the victim was asleep.
they disemboweled him.

211
00:26:00.659 --> 00:26:04.117
This is intestinal fat
that insulates our intestines.

212
00:26:04.296 --> 00:26:07.788
After the suspects
cut open Lorenzo's belly...

213
00:26:07.966 --> 00:26:11.663
...they took out his intestines.
washed them with water...

214
00:26:11.836 --> 00:26:15.101
...replaced them and sewed him up.

215
00:26:19.210 --> 00:26:23.078
He lasted at least two hours
before he died.

216
00:26:23.715 --> 00:26:26.115
It looks as though
he had been held down...

217
00:26:26.384 --> 00:26:29.945
...but his wrists
have sustained no injuries.

218
00:26:37.762 --> 00:26:40.663
Now will you still say those people...

219
00:26:41.466 --> 00:26:44.094
...died naturally of heart attacks?

220
00:26:46.938 --> 00:26:47.439
After an initial investigation.
we have discovered that...

221
00:26:47.439 --> 00:26:50.772
After an initial investigation.
we have discovered that...

222
00:26:50.942 --> 00:26:55.845
...the deaths of Father Lorenzo.
the chairman of Tai Feng...

223
00:26:56.014 --> 00:27:01.179
...and Chiu Miao-fang are
all possibly related.

224
00:27:01.519 --> 00:27:04.818
These are serial murders.

225
00:27:04.990 --> 00:27:06.457
Because this case...

226
00:27:09.194 --> 00:27:11.253
Let the chief finish.

227
00:27:11.463 --> 00:27:15.957
Because this case
has generated many rumors...

228
00:27:16.201 --> 00:27:19.432
...causing anxiety among our society...

229
00:27:19.604 --> 00:27:23.540
...our police force wishes
to solve this crime logically.

230
00:27:23.708 --> 00:27:27.269
Through the American Institute
in Taiwan...

231
00:27:27.445 --> 00:27:32.610
...the FBI has agreed to send an agent
specializing in serial murder...

232
00:27:32.817 --> 00:27:35.285
...to Taiwan to assist
in solving this case.

233
00:27:35.620 --> 00:27:40.887
We hope he can use a scientific method
to move us forward.

234
00:27:41.993 --> 00:27:43.483
Chief...

235
00:27:43.795 --> 00:27:45.854
A question from Miss Chow. please.

236
00:27:46.531 --> 00:27:49.432
Are you giving in
to political pressure?

237
00:27:49.634 --> 00:27:53.331
Also. what about Taiwan's
judicial independence?

238
00:27:53.772 --> 00:27:57.037
Everyone. I am announcing that...

239
00:27:57.375 --> 00:28:02.142
...this FBI investigator doesn't
have the right to bear arms. arrest...

240
00:28:02.380 --> 00:28:04.439
...nor interrogate.

241
00:28:04.783 --> 00:28:07.581
The legal investigation rights
are clear.

242
00:28:07.986 --> 00:28:12.150
Rumors say there are talismans on
the corpse. Was it a cult ritual?

243
00:28:12.323 --> 00:28:14.382
No such thing.

244
00:28:14.592 --> 00:28:16.583
What's the name of the agent?

245
00:28:19.197 --> 00:28:21.722
His name is Kevin Richter.

246
00:28:23.168 --> 00:28:24.567
- How do you spell that?
- How do you spell that?

247
00:28:24.769 --> 00:28:26.202
- How do you spell that?
- How do you spell that?

248
00:28:26.438 --> 00:28:30.772
R-l-C-H-T-E-R.

249
00:28:56.201 --> 00:28:57.225
Bye.

250
00:29:32.837 --> 00:29:33.735
What a nut!

251
00:29:35.340 --> 00:29:36.898
That was my husband.

252
00:29:43.515 --> 00:29:44.982
What is the murderer like?

253
00:29:45.150 --> 00:29:48.176
Are there any political agendas
for your trip?

254
00:29:48.486 --> 00:29:49.680
Do you speak Chinese?

255
00:29:49.854 --> 00:29:53.381
How will you investigate
without speaking Chinese?

256
00:29:55.960 --> 00:29:58.952
Do you know an officer
named Huang Huo-tu?

257
00:30:40.905 --> 00:30:43.339
You want to listen to some music?

258
00:30:44.676 --> 00:30:47.110
And ruin this conversation?

259
00:30:51.316 --> 00:30:53.181
Yeah. sure. Fine with me.

260
00:31:35.693 --> 00:31:38.753
FBI AGENT ARRIVES IN TAIWAN
MYSTERY MAKES INTL. SPOTLIGHT

261
00:32:40.024 --> 00:32:41.548
Morning.

262
00:32:58.843 --> 00:33:02.006
The same mold was
found in the brains...

263
00:33:02.213 --> 00:33:03.805
...and nasal cavities of the victims.

264
00:33:03.982 --> 00:33:07.850
Whether it's toxic and how it entered
the bodies of the victims...

265
00:33:08.019 --> 00:33:10.613
...will depend on the report
from America.

266
00:33:12.123 --> 00:33:14.523
There are no obvious motives
to the murders.

267
00:33:14.692 --> 00:33:17.217
And they did not know one another.

268
00:33:17.528 --> 00:33:19.826
On the body of the third victim...

269
00:33:19.998 --> 00:33:23.126
...a Taoist talisman painted
with the victim's blood.

270
00:33:23.301 --> 00:33:25.792
We have checked
with the Taoist Society.

271
00:33:26.004 --> 00:33:27.665
They've never seen it before.

272
00:33:28.006 --> 00:33:29.200
It should be related to Taoism.

273
00:33:29.574 --> 00:33:33.271
Yes. I wanted to... Excuse me.
Hold on...

274
00:33:35.279 --> 00:33:36.211
I'm sorry.

275
00:33:36.381 --> 00:33:38.872
Tell them they shouldn't count on...

276
00:33:39.117 --> 00:33:40.345
...a Taoist organization for help.

277
00:33:40.518 --> 00:33:42.611
He said we shouldn't
have done that.

278
00:33:42.854 --> 00:33:46.620
What we want is an expert.
a scholar...

279
00:33:46.824 --> 00:33:50.726
...in religious studies
from a university maybe. or...

280
00:33:52.597 --> 00:33:54.758
He said we should ask a scholar.

281
00:33:58.569 --> 00:33:59.934
That's it.

282
00:34:00.905 --> 00:34:02.338
Did you explain how. how...?

283
00:34:05.309 --> 00:34:08.745
Okay. All right. look. this is...

284
00:34:09.914 --> 00:34:13.577
Do we know why the killer
picked these victims?

285
00:34:13.785 --> 00:34:17.186
Anyone know why the victims
were chosen?

286
00:34:17.922 --> 00:34:21.449
It seems to me that's the top priority
of our investigation.

287
00:34:21.759 --> 00:34:23.249
Everything else is a waste of time.

288
00:34:23.428 --> 00:34:24.952
Everything else is a waste of time.

289
00:34:25.129 --> 00:34:27.893
Didn't we just say
there's no obvious motive?

290
00:34:28.132 --> 00:34:30.623
Is this material from a textbook?

291
00:34:30.868 --> 00:34:33.302
Why come all the way
to tell us this?

292
00:34:33.471 --> 00:34:35.939
Who is in charge?
Who is in charge?

293
00:34:36.574 --> 00:34:39.805
All right. stop it.

294
00:34:41.446 --> 00:34:43.038
What are they saying?

295
00:34:44.282 --> 00:34:47.217
"Thank you." and they'll
consider your suggestions.

296
00:34:50.254 --> 00:34:51.744
I can see that.

297
00:34:52.056 --> 00:34:53.421
That's all for today.

298
00:34:53.691 --> 00:34:54.715
No questions. right?

299
00:34:54.892 --> 00:34:55.984
That's it for today.

300
00:34:56.761 --> 00:35:01.198
If someone can take me
to Lorenzo's murder scene...

301
00:35:01.399 --> 00:35:03.196
How tall can a person get?

302
00:35:10.775 --> 00:35:13.335
I had these blessed for our safety.

303
00:35:13.544 --> 00:35:15.569
Sit down. Sit down.

304
00:35:19.417 --> 00:35:21.180
- Excuse me.
- What. what?

305
00:35:21.385 --> 00:35:23.250
Sit down. please.

306
00:35:26.424 --> 00:35:29.052
He wants to go
to Lorenzo's murder scene.

307
00:35:29.260 --> 00:35:31.785
Not necessary. We checked
everything out in detail.

308
00:35:31.963 --> 00:35:32.952
And took photographs.

309
00:35:33.164 --> 00:35:34.529
He says it's not necessary.

310
00:35:34.732 --> 00:35:35.960
Bullshit.

311
00:35:39.137 --> 00:35:40.729
That's bullshit.

312
00:35:42.273 --> 00:35:43.740
Go ahead. translate it.

313
00:35:43.941 --> 00:35:46.034
- I don't have to. They know.
- Good.

314
00:35:46.244 --> 00:35:47.768
It's very necessary.

315
00:35:47.979 --> 00:35:50.675
It's what I do.
It's why I'm here.

316
00:35:57.421 --> 00:35:58.683
You take him there.

317
00:35:59.524 --> 00:36:02.982
But I don't know anything about this.

318
00:36:04.829 --> 00:36:07.195
- He said it's okay.
- Good.

319
00:36:08.499 --> 00:36:10.262
Well. then...

320
00:36:11.369 --> 00:36:12.734
Thank your mother.

321
00:36:15.740 --> 00:36:17.367
Thank your mother.

322
00:36:19.210 --> 00:36:20.199
We. we...

323
00:36:20.378 --> 00:36:23.040
It's "Thank you very much." right?

324
00:36:23.281 --> 00:36:24.543
Right.

325
00:36:27.451 --> 00:36:29.442
This is Taoist. isn't it?

326
00:36:31.589 --> 00:36:33.420
Can I offer advice?

327
00:36:33.691 --> 00:36:37.787
You should be more respectful.
Not talk so much.

328
00:36:38.196 --> 00:36:39.527
Thanks.

329
00:36:40.565 --> 00:36:43.398
I'll consider your suggestion.

330
00:36:46.137 --> 00:36:47.570
You are a foreigner.

331
00:36:48.573 --> 00:36:52.168
I'm saying. if you don't
want to cause trouble.

332
00:36:52.343 --> 00:36:54.402
I'm surprised at you. Huo-tu.

333
00:36:55.346 --> 00:36:58.008
I didn't figure you
for the cautious type.

334
00:36:58.816 --> 00:37:01.512
- That's not your reputation.
- What do you mean?

335
00:37:18.102 --> 00:37:19.569
You researched my background?

336
00:37:20.004 --> 00:37:22.199
I like to know my partners.

337
00:37:22.440 --> 00:37:25.568
This story is why
the AIT recommended you.

338
00:37:25.776 --> 00:37:28.836
They don't have much confidence
in your police force.

339
00:37:29.513 --> 00:37:31.242
They got it all wrong.

340
00:37:32.049 --> 00:37:35.610
I'm no different than any other
policeman on the force.

341
00:37:35.786 --> 00:37:39.085
And I regret very much
my naive behavior.

342
00:37:40.958 --> 00:37:44.121
What do you have to say
about your corruption trial?

343
00:37:54.839 --> 00:37:58.070
Huang Huo-tu. you bastard!

344
00:37:58.376 --> 00:38:00.503
How can you sleep at night?

345
00:38:00.711 --> 00:38:03.544
What kind of cousin are you?

346
00:38:03.814 --> 00:38:04.872
Officer Huang!

347
00:38:09.954 --> 00:38:11.148
Watch out!

348
00:38:22.933 --> 00:38:27.495
Listen. I was assigned to this case.
I got no choice.

349
00:38:27.672 --> 00:38:31.005
And you are not going to get
any special treatment from me.

350
00:38:32.843 --> 00:38:34.140
Got it.

351
00:38:34.979 --> 00:38:37.971
Do me a favor and try
not to kill me. okay?

352
00:38:59.270 --> 00:39:02.205
So this is where the dead guy was?

353
00:39:02.373 --> 00:39:03.601
Yes.

354
00:39:07.878 --> 00:39:12.645
- What's this?
- Lung Chi-ji. air conditioner.

355
00:39:17.888 --> 00:39:19.879
Let's just see.

356
00:39:26.597 --> 00:39:30.727
Were there air conditioners
at the other crime scenes?

357
00:39:32.169 --> 00:39:36.799
The whole city has them.
It's hot. Why?

358
00:39:42.780 --> 00:39:44.748
Do you have any idea...

359
00:39:46.517 --> 00:39:48.007
...what this is?

360
00:39:51.889 --> 00:39:54.619
This is the pellet found
in Lorenzo's room.

361
00:39:54.892 --> 00:39:58.623
This is from Chiu Miao-fang's
air conditioner.

362
00:39:59.263 --> 00:40:04.200
This was found on the floor
of Chairman Liao's office.

363
00:40:07.138 --> 00:40:10.266
They were from the same device.

364
00:40:11.041 --> 00:40:15.535
- What device?
- Possibly a converted air rifle.

365
00:40:15.746 --> 00:40:18.943
- These people are amazing.
- Why do you say that?

366
00:40:19.150 --> 00:40:22.244
To hollow out
and drill three holes...

367
00:40:22.453 --> 00:40:25.251
...requires advanced technology.

368
00:40:25.489 --> 00:40:26.956
Besides...

369
00:40:28.159 --> 00:40:29.421
...Iook...

370
00:40:29.627 --> 00:40:33.063
...it's the same bacteria
found in the victims.

371
00:40:33.230 --> 00:40:38.600
So the killers put the mold
into the hollowed-out pellets...

372
00:40:39.069 --> 00:40:42.596
...then shot them into
the air-conditioning vents...

373
00:40:42.840 --> 00:40:45.308
...for the bacteria to dissipate.
- Correct.

374
00:40:58.189 --> 00:40:59.588
How are you?

375
00:41:01.459 --> 00:41:03.450
Hello there. how you doing?

376
00:41:06.730 --> 00:41:07.924
What's the matter?

377
00:41:08.399 --> 00:41:09.798
You shy?

378
00:41:11.135 --> 00:41:13.126
Well. I'm just wondering...

379
00:41:13.471 --> 00:41:16.929
...what you're doing here
all by yourself.

380
00:41:19.043 --> 00:41:21.910
My name is Kevin.

381
00:41:26.283 --> 00:41:27.307
Yours?

382
00:41:28.219 --> 00:41:29.982
- What's your...?
- Her name is Mei-mei.

383
00:41:33.390 --> 00:41:35.051
She's my daughter.

384
00:41:35.493 --> 00:41:38.587
I was just trying
to make her smile.

385
00:41:39.263 --> 00:41:42.426
I apologize.
She's scared of strangers.

386
00:41:42.633 --> 00:41:44.624
Not at all.
You taught her right.

387
00:41:45.736 --> 00:41:47.761
- Kevin Richter.
- I know.

388
00:41:48.138 --> 00:41:53.166
- I'm the wife of Officer Huang Huo-tu.
- Oh. really?

389
00:41:53.544 --> 00:41:55.910
- It's a pleasure to meet you.
- Me too.

390
00:41:56.146 --> 00:41:57.670
Your husband. He's a...

391
00:41:57.948 --> 00:41:59.381
You know. he's...

392
00:42:00.584 --> 00:42:03.144
He's a very interesting guy.

393
00:42:03.487 --> 00:42:05.421
Yeah. he is.

394
00:42:06.557 --> 00:42:08.320
Thank you for lying.

395
00:42:09.460 --> 00:42:10.392
Anytime.

396
00:42:10.594 --> 00:42:10.628
Remember how I turned up
at Tai Feng...

397
00:42:10.628 --> 00:42:12.823
Remember how I turned up
at Tai Feng...

398
00:42:13.063 --> 00:42:16.055
...to arrest an illegal
foreign worker?

399
00:42:17.334 --> 00:42:18.596
Well?

400
00:42:19.570 --> 00:42:21.504
I found out from the papers...

401
00:42:22.773 --> 00:42:25.139
...I checked the other two victims.

402
00:42:25.409 --> 00:42:28.105
They were in the papers
and were killed thereafter.

403
00:42:28.279 --> 00:42:33.342
TAI FENG DUMPS TO XIC WASTE
ILLEGAL LABORER WON'T TESTIFY

404
00:42:33.517 --> 00:42:37.146
Huo-tu. I have to tell you one thing.

405
00:42:38.789 --> 00:42:42.748
Chief is concerned about that FBI man.
You must be careful.

406
00:42:43.994 --> 00:42:45.689
Have you thought that...

407
00:42:46.030 --> 00:42:48.692
...no matter what this Richter...

408
00:42:48.866 --> 00:42:52.996
...comes up with in the end or not...

409
00:42:53.270 --> 00:42:55.932
...your life will be different?

410
00:42:56.507 --> 00:42:57.769
Think about it.

411
00:42:57.975 --> 00:43:02.139
Let's say. because of him.
the case really does move ahead.

412
00:43:02.379 --> 00:43:05.507
How do you think the men will feel?

413
00:43:08.886 --> 00:43:11.787
You will be even worse off.

414
00:43:14.325 --> 00:43:17.226
He was called in just to do a show.

415
00:43:17.461 --> 00:43:20.294
Just help him finish his show.

416
00:43:22.566 --> 00:43:23.863
Besides...

417
00:43:25.336 --> 00:43:29.329
I don't think the chief believes
this case can be cracked.

418
00:43:29.740 --> 00:43:33.574
Just watch.
He'll be looking for a scapegoat.

419
00:43:34.678 --> 00:43:38.045
- It can't be cracked?
- Are you an idiot?

420
00:43:38.315 --> 00:43:40.306
Use your head.

421
00:43:41.352 --> 00:43:43.718
This is not even a normal case.

422
00:43:45.522 --> 00:43:47.683
How many years since the academy?

423
00:43:47.891 --> 00:43:51.520
Twenty? Have you seen
such a thing in 20 years?

424
00:43:52.830 --> 00:43:55.298
Or heard anything like it?

425
00:43:57.134 --> 00:43:58.431
Let me tell you...

426
00:43:59.169 --> 00:44:04.630
...it may not have been
committed by a human.

427
00:44:08.612 --> 00:44:10.671
Now you've gone too far.

428
00:44:11.148 --> 00:44:14.879
Today I stand in the position
of your friend...

429
00:44:15.152 --> 00:44:18.053
...although being your friend
sure as hell isn't easy...

430
00:44:18.288 --> 00:44:20.051
...I still must tell you...

431
00:44:20.391 --> 00:44:23.622
...you are facing
a hopeless chess game.

432
00:44:23.827 --> 00:44:26.557
The best way is to give up...

433
00:44:26.797 --> 00:44:28.856
...and save your own skin.

434
00:44:37.207 --> 00:44:41.371
You mean she hasn't
spoken in two years?

435
00:44:43.213 --> 00:44:47.377
- Not one word?
- Nothing. Ever since the incident.

436
00:44:48.385 --> 00:44:52.253
You're talking about the abduction?

437
00:44:54.091 --> 00:44:56.582
- I'm sorry.
- It's okay.

438
00:45:00.130 --> 00:45:01.495
What's going on?

439
00:45:08.439 --> 00:45:11.272
Don't lose it again.
Each copy costs $ 150.

440
00:45:11.542 --> 00:45:16.206
I am busy. When I'm done.
I'll complete the application.

441
00:45:16.613 --> 00:45:20.276
You're too busy to sign your name?

442
00:45:23.220 --> 00:45:24.881
I have to make arrangements.

443
00:45:25.155 --> 00:45:27.350
What have you done
for the past two years?

444
00:45:30.894 --> 00:45:35.331
I spoke with my parents.
You won't have to be responsible.

445
00:45:37.801 --> 00:45:38.961
And our daughter?

446
00:45:39.636 --> 00:45:43.299
I'll bring her to Canada.
They have specialists there.

447
00:45:43.741 --> 00:45:45.971
She needs help.

448
00:45:46.543 --> 00:45:50.274
- She has a whole life ahead of her.
- Very well.

449
00:45:50.481 --> 00:45:52.312
Thanks for taking the trouble.

450
00:45:54.685 --> 00:45:56.312
Let's go. Mei-mei.

451
00:45:58.422 --> 00:46:01.289
- It was nice to meet you.
- Pleasure was all mine.

452
00:46:02.593 --> 00:46:06.359
- And good luck. You will need it.
- Thank you. Bye-bye.

453
00:46:06.597 --> 00:46:07.586
Bye-bye.

454
00:46:14.838 --> 00:46:16.601
ACADEMIA SINICA

455
00:46:17.841 --> 00:46:20.207
DR. SHENG ZU CHANG.
SOCIAL ANTHROPOLOG Y

456
00:46:32.222 --> 00:46:33.382
Amazing.

457
00:46:33.824 --> 00:46:36.520
This talisman is fairly new.

458
00:46:37.461 --> 00:46:39.520
Several years ago...

459
00:46:39.797 --> 00:46:43.699
...a Taoist temple was unearthed
in Jiao Chi. China...

460
00:46:43.901 --> 00:46:45.869
...called the True Sage Temple.

461
00:46:46.503 --> 00:46:51.839
Inside. they discovered writing
carved into the stone.

462
00:46:52.075 --> 00:46:56.307
Some religious implements
and talismanic relics.

463
00:46:57.648 --> 00:47:00.048
These are the photographs.

464
00:47:33.383 --> 00:47:34.645
This way. please.

465
00:47:56.139 --> 00:47:59.233
TRUE SAGE TEMPLE

466
00:47:59.776 --> 00:48:02.108
Do you understand?

467
00:48:03.113 --> 00:48:05.138
The talisman on
the foreigner's body...

468
00:48:05.482 --> 00:48:09.475
...is the same as those
discovered a few years ago.

469
00:48:09.686 --> 00:48:12.382
- What does the talisman represent?
- Gou Di.

470
00:48:12.856 --> 00:48:14.414
Gou Di?

471
00:48:14.691 --> 00:48:17.023
A summons to the underworld.

472
00:48:17.394 --> 00:48:21.592
A death curse
from the king of hell.

473
00:49:00.971 --> 00:49:02.666
FRIGID HELL

474
00:49:07.010 --> 00:49:09.308
TONGUE-REMOVAL HELL

475
00:49:10.714 --> 00:49:12.705
DISEMBOWELMENT HELL

476
00:49:16.553 --> 00:49:18.350
HEART-EXTRACTING HELL

477
00:49:51.154 --> 00:49:54.214
And the stone carvings...

478
00:49:54.458 --> 00:50:00.055
It is all in code.
We don't know what they mean...

479
00:50:00.230 --> 00:50:04.826
...we can't make out the text.
It's a complete puzzle.

480
00:50:07.437 --> 00:50:09.769
This is a copy of the same scriptures
in modern characters.

481
00:50:10.674 --> 00:50:14.872
But they still don't make any sense.

482
00:50:15.245 --> 00:50:18.043
- What about these diagrams?
- They're common.

483
00:50:18.448 --> 00:50:20.780
They're basic Taoist visions.

484
00:50:21.752 --> 00:50:23.982
Taoism believes that
through this system...

485
00:50:24.154 --> 00:50:26.520
...it's possible to see
into the past and future.

486
00:50:26.890 --> 00:50:28.881
It depicts
the universe of Taoism.

487
00:50:29.159 --> 00:50:34.153
Mahjong and Chinese chess...

488
00:50:34.331 --> 00:50:36.060
...through minor examples...

489
00:50:36.533 --> 00:50:39.991
...have also evolved
from these diagrams.

490
00:52:24.241 --> 00:52:25.902
I brought the markings.

491
00:52:27.043 --> 00:52:29.477
And if you put it on top the scripture...

492
00:52:30.981 --> 00:52:33.074
...they encircle Chinese characters.

493
00:52:34.251 --> 00:52:37.516
This one. Fu.
would mean "Liao Zheng Fu."

494
00:52:37.954 --> 00:52:41.219
And Miao would mean "Chiu Miao-fang."

495
00:52:41.658 --> 00:52:43.683
They happen to be the first two victims.

496
00:52:44.728 --> 00:52:46.525
And this one. Jing...

497
00:52:47.297 --> 00:52:48.889
...that one's more abstract.

498
00:52:49.833 --> 00:52:52.267
Perhaps it has something to do
with the fact that...

499
00:52:52.469 --> 00:52:54.903
...Lorenzo was a Christian pastor.

500
00:52:55.472 --> 00:52:58.908
When Christianity was
first introduced to China...

501
00:52:59.876 --> 00:53:03.437
...it was referred to as
the Jing religion.

502
00:53:04.814 --> 00:53:07.305
So our guy's using this pattern...

503
00:53:08.685 --> 00:53:10.346
...to search out the victims?

504
00:53:10.887 --> 00:53:14.288
All we can say. he's fulfilling
a thousand-year-old prophecy.

505
00:53:19.829 --> 00:53:21.626
You see this one?

506
00:53:23.099 --> 00:53:27.559
"The ones who don't believe in God."

507
00:53:28.171 --> 00:53:30.401
Which means "the nonbeliever."

508
00:53:34.511 --> 00:53:35.876
And this one is...

509
00:53:36.112 --> 00:53:41.914
..."yin and yang."

510
00:53:43.220 --> 00:53:45.518
All these are from the same diagram.

511
00:53:47.123 --> 00:53:50.581
Next victim could be a Wong.

512
00:53:53.496 --> 00:53:55.555
If according to this.

513
00:54:00.670 --> 00:54:02.262
Phil? Can we get on with it?

514
00:54:04.307 --> 00:54:07.333
We're still not sure how to interpret
the evidence you sent us.

515
00:54:08.311 --> 00:54:09.778
However. we're sure of one thing.

516
00:54:10.247 --> 00:54:13.614
The mold in the victims' brains
isn't mold after all.

517
00:54:13.783 --> 00:54:16.911
It's a hybrid life form.

518
00:54:17.587 --> 00:54:19.077
A bug-born fungus.

519
00:54:20.490 --> 00:54:23.391
It's a variety
we haven't seen before.

520
00:54:23.893 --> 00:54:28.159
This is a kind of mite.
And these spores attach themselves.

521
00:54:28.565 --> 00:54:32.057
So you're saying mites
carry the fungus to the brain?

522
00:54:32.302 --> 00:54:35.999
Exactly. These insects seek out
the body warmth of living organisms.

523
00:54:36.172 --> 00:54:38.470
They'll find a host...

524
00:54:38.675 --> 00:54:41.269
...especially in small.
contained spaces.

525
00:54:41.478 --> 00:54:46.177
That's why the killer shot the fungus
into the a/c units. Very smart.

526
00:54:46.549 --> 00:54:48.016
The mites enter through the nose...

527
00:54:48.184 --> 00:54:51.676
...find their way up to the warm
brain and embed themselves.

528
00:54:52.289 --> 00:54:54.723
The victim doesn't feel a thing.

529
00:54:54.924 --> 00:54:58.052
But were you able
to establish cause of death?

530
00:55:00.030 --> 00:55:01.224
Yes and no.

531
00:55:01.398 --> 00:55:03.628
We found high amounts of serotonin...

532
00:55:03.800 --> 00:55:05.995
...and dopamine in the victims' blood.

533
00:55:06.169 --> 00:55:07.466
What's dopamine?

534
00:55:08.571 --> 00:55:10.937
A naturally occurring chemical.

535
00:55:11.207 --> 00:55:12.196
Same as morphine.

536
00:55:12.375 --> 00:55:13.535
How much is "high"?

537
00:55:13.743 --> 00:55:15.973
- Are those elements toxic?
- Not usually.

538
00:55:16.212 --> 00:55:17.873
Just the opposite. in fact.

539
00:55:18.081 --> 00:55:20.242
It's considered to be healing.

540
00:55:20.483 --> 00:55:23.714
The amount in the victims' blood
is about 50.000 times...

541
00:55:23.987 --> 00:55:26.285
...any previously recorded count.

542
00:55:26.556 --> 00:55:30.356
To secrete this amount. you'd
have to do a ton of cocaine...

543
00:55:30.627 --> 00:55:33.687
...and then have an orgasm
that lasts 40 years.

544
00:55:34.164 --> 00:55:35.631
What a way to go.

545
00:55:37.267 --> 00:55:41.135
So you're saying the dopamine...

546
00:55:41.338 --> 00:55:44.466
...made the victims feel
like they were drowning...

547
00:55:44.641 --> 00:55:46.666
...or being consumed by fire?

548
00:55:47.143 --> 00:55:50.738
Well. it could. Just like what
drugs do to the brain.

549
00:55:52.048 --> 00:55:54.778
- Why different hallucinations?
- Yeah. why?

550
00:55:55.585 --> 00:55:58.679
Do you mean the killer
can control their delusions?

551
00:56:03.460 --> 00:56:05.451
Actually. we don't know.

552
00:56:05.695 --> 00:56:08.061
None of this has ever been studied.

553
00:56:24.881 --> 00:56:26.678
Only $ 100?

554
00:56:26.850 --> 00:56:29.546
- You can't give me two extra?
- The boss says no.

555
00:56:31.488 --> 00:56:35.982
- When do you get off tonight?
- I'll tell if you buy more.

556
00:56:36.192 --> 00:56:38.956
- Then give me a Mild Seven.
- Okay. Wait here.

557
00:56:44.334 --> 00:56:46.461
Do you need anything else?

558
00:56:50.039 --> 00:56:53.099
- What is your name?
- I'm Xiao Ya.

559
00:56:56.279 --> 00:56:59.715
- Shit. what are you honking about?
- I'll pick you up later.

560
00:57:07.390 --> 00:57:08.482
Huo-tu!

561
00:57:17.066 --> 00:57:18.158
Where to?

562
00:57:18.802 --> 00:57:19.996
Scene of a murder.

563
00:57:21.070 --> 00:57:22.662
This is from two days ago.

564
00:57:22.839 --> 00:57:24.306
The victim is Chen Liang-wang.

565
00:57:24.808 --> 00:57:27.436
His parents committed suicide.

566
00:57:27.911 --> 00:57:29.742
We called his home to check it out.

567
00:57:29.979 --> 00:57:33.244
They said he went to a seance
at a Taoist temple.

568
00:57:33.450 --> 00:57:36.351
He felt his parents had hid
his inheritance from him.

569
00:57:36.586 --> 00:57:38.679
Do we know which temple?

570
00:57:39.789 --> 00:57:41.086
I called to ask.

571
00:57:41.324 --> 00:57:44.452
There are at least 1000
temples around here.

572
00:57:53.236 --> 00:57:56.433
Li. long time no see!
What are you doing here?

573
00:57:56.706 --> 00:57:58.731
- We're here to visit you!
- Stop it!

574
00:57:58.942 --> 00:58:02.241
You are in the media everywhere.

575
00:58:02.479 --> 00:58:04.640
It's a pain in the ass.

576
00:58:04.814 --> 00:58:08.443
They're injured.
Gangsters of this neighborhood.

577
00:58:08.985 --> 00:58:12.887
- Is there a Chen Liang-wang?
- He's over there.

578
00:58:13.056 --> 00:58:14.148
What's the situation?

579
00:58:14.390 --> 00:58:19.157
A girl saw two bald guys
get into an argument over traffic.

580
00:58:19.395 --> 00:58:22.091
People came to watch.
and the van couldn't move.

581
00:58:22.298 --> 00:58:24.766
No one saw what actually happened.

582
00:58:25.001 --> 00:58:26.593
The bald guys killed the gangster?

583
00:58:30.406 --> 00:58:32.670
Looks like we got our fourth victim.

584
00:58:36.079 --> 00:58:40.413
He took a gun and suddenly
there was a loud scream.

585
00:58:40.650 --> 00:58:44.518
I couldn't see what they were doing.

586
00:58:44.787 --> 00:58:47.915
And things got confusing.

587
00:58:48.124 --> 00:58:52.959
A lot of people came over to watch...

588
00:58:53.196 --> 00:58:54.288
Richter.

589
00:59:11.681 --> 00:59:13.740
You okay with your noodles?

590
00:59:14.951 --> 00:59:19.945
- I hope they're not too hot for you.
- No. they're spicy.

591
00:59:21.524 --> 00:59:23.685
I'm from Texas. I like spicy food.

592
00:59:23.893 --> 00:59:28.125
Oh. yes? Then add more of this.
You'll like it.

593
00:59:31.734 --> 00:59:32.962
Thank you.

594
00:59:35.972 --> 00:59:37.496
I've been wondering.

595
00:59:38.741 --> 00:59:41.039
That bag of yours in the car...

596
00:59:42.812 --> 00:59:44.473
Are you religious?

597
00:59:45.548 --> 00:59:47.573
It's not relevant what I am.

598
00:59:55.191 --> 00:59:56.590
We are convinced...

599
00:59:56.826 --> 00:59:58.987
...that something impure could...

600
00:59:59.195 --> 01:00:01.527
...be lurking anywhere.
- Impure?

601
01:00:02.532 --> 01:00:04.966
Evil spirits. ghosts.

602
01:00:06.135 --> 01:00:09.627
The altar or the red bag is
for peace and prosperity.

603
01:00:09.839 --> 01:00:12.501
Most people believe in them.

604
01:00:13.610 --> 01:00:15.339
You haven't answered yet.

605
01:00:15.545 --> 01:00:17.035
Do you believe in them?

606
01:00:19.115 --> 01:00:20.980
We just don't understand...

607
01:00:21.184 --> 01:00:24.176
...why you can't see evil.
- We see it.

608
01:00:25.888 --> 01:00:29.016
- We lock it up sometimes.
- That's impossible.

609
01:00:29.192 --> 01:00:32.320
Look. I rely on science.

610
01:00:32.996 --> 01:00:35.829
Not talismans. not good-luck charms.

611
01:00:37.567 --> 01:00:40.035
Your so-called scientific methods...

612
01:00:40.236 --> 01:00:44.172
...are only useful when dealing
with mortals like ourselves.

613
01:00:44.574 --> 01:00:47.509
There are beings that cannot be
controlled by our laws.

614
01:00:47.710 --> 01:00:49.109
What are you saying?

615
01:00:51.414 --> 01:00:55.145
Are you saying that the killer
is an evil spirit...

616
01:00:57.420 --> 01:00:59.115
...or some kind of...

617
01:01:00.423 --> 01:01:02.152
...something from another world?

618
01:01:02.492 --> 01:01:04.551
What's wrong with you. Mr. Richter?

619
01:01:05.862 --> 01:01:08.092
In all your years with the FBI...

620
01:01:08.564 --> 01:01:11.260
...you have never encountered a demon?

621
01:01:18.941 --> 01:01:20.704
Now I see why you have a hard time...

622
01:01:20.877 --> 01:01:23.368
...fitting in with
your fellow officers.

623
01:01:27.383 --> 01:01:29.214
You're going to profile me?

624
01:01:30.920 --> 01:01:32.353
I am a suspect now?

625
01:01:49.472 --> 01:01:54.739
I may be a foreigner. but there
are some things that are universal.

626
01:01:56.212 --> 01:02:01.240
What you are doing to your family.
and yourself. I've seen it before.

627
01:02:03.586 --> 01:02:06.885
You gave me some advice before.
I'll return the favor.

628
01:02:07.090 --> 01:02:08.717
You're a brave man.

629
01:02:10.326 --> 01:02:12.692
You could be a great police officer.

630
01:02:14.597 --> 01:02:17.725
You exposed major corruption.
That took courage.

631
01:02:18.534 --> 01:02:20.434
- Courage?
- That's right. Courage.

632
01:02:20.703 --> 01:02:22.694
And that's in any language.

633
01:02:24.841 --> 01:02:28.777
Now you're just torturing yourself.

634
01:02:29.545 --> 01:02:32.173
Not many men
could've done what you did.

635
01:02:32.381 --> 01:02:35.077
You let your colleagues
treat you like a joke.

636
01:02:35.284 --> 01:02:36.683
You welcome it.

637
01:02:37.286 --> 01:02:40.847
You hide out in that office
and let your marriage go to shit.

638
01:02:43.292 --> 01:02:46.693
I've never fired a shot
since I joined the force.

639
01:02:47.530 --> 01:02:49.555
And I've never been under fire.

640
01:02:50.399 --> 01:02:52.026
But my daughter did...

641
01:02:52.668 --> 01:02:54.533
...by my own wife's cousin.

642
01:02:55.872 --> 01:02:59.364
And I just did nothing.
I did nothing to stop it.

643
01:02:59.575 --> 01:03:02.510
- Daddy!
- Don't come over!

644
01:03:03.045 --> 01:03:06.071
Put the gun down.
Put the gun down!

645
01:03:06.349 --> 01:03:07.873
- Yuan!
- Put your gun down.

646
01:03:09.552 --> 01:03:10.484
Put it down!

647
01:03:10.686 --> 01:03:13.177
- I've been sentenced to 15 years!
- Daddy.

648
01:03:13.389 --> 01:03:14.583
Mei-mei!

649
01:03:14.824 --> 01:03:17.418
I gave my life to the police force
for 15 years in jail?

650
01:03:17.660 --> 01:03:19.992
Yuan. don't do that.

651
01:03:20.229 --> 01:03:21.662
She is your own niece!

652
01:03:21.864 --> 01:03:24.389
We can appeal!

653
01:03:26.569 --> 01:03:28.332
We can still appeal!

654
01:03:28.571 --> 01:03:31.540
It's useless.
So what if I took the money?

655
01:03:31.707 --> 01:03:33.504
Think clearly about it.

656
01:03:33.743 --> 01:03:37.201
Huo-tu. Are you really so clean?

657
01:03:37.380 --> 01:03:40.543
You can't bear to see
someone have a better life?

658
01:03:42.819 --> 01:03:44.878
Your daddy forced me to do this.

659
01:03:52.094 --> 01:03:54.085
No!

660
01:04:01.771 --> 01:04:04.899
His aim was off.
The bullet grazed her.

661
01:04:05.675 --> 01:04:09.338
The doctor said she was unharmed
and would be fine.

662
01:04:10.546 --> 01:04:11.843
But he was wrong.

663
01:04:13.316 --> 01:04:16.581
Like you. he thought only of science.

664
01:04:23.226 --> 01:04:25.160
You asked what I believe in.

665
01:04:26.929 --> 01:04:29.921
I believe that she saw
something evil that day.

666
01:04:30.399 --> 01:04:32.026
And ever since...

667
01:04:32.735 --> 01:04:34.999
...she's been unable to speak again.

668
01:05:07.003 --> 01:05:08.061
Who is it?

669
01:05:08.237 --> 01:05:10.899
My name is Huang.
I'm looking for Dr. Sheng.

670
01:05:11.140 --> 01:05:14.268
Do you know what time it is?
Dr. Sheng has gone to bed.

671
01:05:14.443 --> 01:05:18.743
I'm sorry. I am a police officer.
This is urgent.

672
01:05:28.224 --> 01:05:32.718
This guy wants to attain immortality.
Why didn't you show me this before?

673
01:05:33.396 --> 01:05:34.488
Attain immortality?

674
01:05:34.697 --> 01:05:39.157
One branch of Taoism theorized
there are five kinds of hell.

675
01:05:39.735 --> 01:05:42.295
There is frigid hell...

676
01:05:42.805 --> 01:05:46.468
...fire hell. disembowelment hell.
heart-extraction hell...

677
01:05:46.676 --> 01:05:48.541
...and tongue-removal hell.

678
01:05:48.744 --> 01:05:52.475
After passing through
these five hells...

679
01:05:52.682 --> 01:05:56.243
...you attain immortality
in the sixth level.

680
01:05:56.519 --> 01:05:59.488
How to pass through the five tortures...

681
01:05:59.689 --> 01:06:03.216
...is something people cannot imagine.

682
01:06:03.492 --> 01:06:07.724
So the murderer killed
in order to attain...

683
01:06:08.164 --> 01:06:09.256
...immortality?

684
01:06:09.498 --> 01:06:11.363
According to history...

685
01:06:11.567 --> 01:06:14.502
...there was a Wong Shang
during the Sung Dynasty...

686
01:06:14.704 --> 01:06:19.164
...who is worshiped in Hong Kong's
Wong Tai Sin Temple.

687
01:06:19.809 --> 01:06:24.439
Before he attained immortality.
he killed many half-humans.

688
01:06:24.647 --> 01:06:28.105
These half-humans are
people who had committed sins...

689
01:06:28.351 --> 01:06:30.376
...and are neither human nor ghost.

690
01:06:30.619 --> 01:06:36.057
He must have used that theory to send
those man-ghosts to hell...

691
01:06:36.292 --> 01:06:38.123
...so he could attain sainthood.

692
01:06:38.894 --> 01:06:41.954
These four victims...

693
01:06:42.131 --> 01:06:45.191
...are presumably all morally corrupt.

694
01:06:45.368 --> 01:06:47.302
It's said that Wong Shang...

695
01:06:47.470 --> 01:06:50.962
...could write talismans
and perform rituals.

696
01:06:51.207 --> 01:06:53.675
He had double pupils.
which enabled him...

697
01:06:53.876 --> 01:06:58.370
...to see a thousand miles by day
and look at spirits by night.

698
01:06:58.681 --> 01:07:00.672
- Double pupils?
- Yes.

699
01:07:01.150 --> 01:07:04.642
Double pupils means...

700
01:07:04.854 --> 01:07:08.551
...that this person has two pupils...

701
01:07:10.259 --> 01:07:12.090
...in one eye.

702
01:07:13.162 --> 01:07:17.292
Only with two pupils
can one locate half-humans.

703
01:07:18.167 --> 01:07:20.431
From looking at his methods...

704
01:07:21.303 --> 01:07:23.794
...your murderer is quite something.

705
01:07:24.006 --> 01:07:28.807
He must have been gravely ill to be
able to distill this kind of potion.

706
01:07:30.546 --> 01:07:34.539
- Why must he be gravely ill?
- According to Taoism...

707
01:07:34.784 --> 01:07:37.480
...grave illness is essential
for attaining immortality.

708
01:07:37.686 --> 01:07:41.679
Only in grave illness can a person
experience real awakening.

709
01:07:43.125 --> 01:07:45.650
Dr. Shang. I found some words.

710
01:07:45.928 --> 01:07:48.954
Yin and yang.
Do you know what that means?

711
01:07:49.532 --> 01:07:51.591
According to the lunar diagram...

712
01:07:52.968 --> 01:07:58.873
...these "Chi" represent
from May to July...

713
01:07:59.375 --> 01:08:02.606
...they also represent
fire. Huo. and earth. Tu.

714
01:08:11.887 --> 01:08:15.220
Excuse me.
Hello?

715
01:08:16.826 --> 01:08:20.762
- Where are you?
- Surfing the Web with some teenagers.

716
01:08:20.930 --> 01:08:23.694
That Styrofoam we found
inside the killer's van?

717
01:08:24.934 --> 01:08:27.596
It's a type of Styrofoam used
to prevent static electricity.

718
01:08:28.704 --> 01:08:30.968
The windows were covered
with a special material.

719
01:08:31.607 --> 01:08:34.599
A heat-isolating layer
shuts out ultraviolet rays.

720
01:08:35.111 --> 01:08:36.806
Now. in the U. S...

721
01:08:37.446 --> 01:08:41.382
...both are used in delivery vans
for integrated-circuit units.

722
01:08:43.352 --> 01:08:47.288
All our evidence points to suspects
with a high-tech industry background.

723
01:08:48.390 --> 01:08:52.622
We're not looking for delivery men.
These guys are highly placed.

724
01:08:59.101 --> 01:09:00.398
Dr. Sheng.

725
01:09:02.538 --> 01:09:03.971
Excuse me for asking.

726
01:09:04.206 --> 01:09:06.766
Do you believe in this
"attaining immortality"?

727
01:09:07.543 --> 01:09:10.273
If I told you yes.
you would immediately...

728
01:09:10.479 --> 01:09:12.037
...doubt my authority.

729
01:09:14.483 --> 01:09:15.745
Officer Huang...

730
01:09:16.085 --> 01:09:18.076
...if you ask me...

731
01:09:18.654 --> 01:09:22.055
...whether I believe in
Taoist immortals...

732
01:09:22.291 --> 01:09:24.555
...or in aliens...

733
01:09:25.227 --> 01:09:27.718
...I would not choose aliens.

734
01:09:37.373 --> 01:09:40.774
This delivery van
belongs to Cutting Edge.

735
01:09:41.010 --> 01:09:42.841
HSINCHU SCIENCE PARK
ADMINISTRATION

736
01:09:43.012 --> 01:09:47.108
- It no longer exists.
- What does that mean?

737
01:09:47.950 --> 01:09:50.885
Cutting Edge was
an IC design company...

738
01:09:51.086 --> 01:09:53.646
...owned by two guys who got
their Ph.D.'s from America.

739
01:09:53.889 --> 01:09:55.720
They made a lot of money.

740
01:09:55.925 --> 01:09:59.122
But they got caught up in religion.

741
01:09:59.328 --> 01:10:03.731
In the end. they sold the company
for $2 billion.

742
01:10:03.999 --> 01:10:08.595
- And the two went off to become monks.
- Do you have any data on them?

743
01:10:10.673 --> 01:10:14.268
It's printing. These people
are really fanatical.

744
01:10:14.443 --> 01:10:17.173
They spent a lot of money
to ship a temple...

745
01:10:17.413 --> 01:10:19.973
...from mainland China.
The whole thing.

746
01:10:20.249 --> 01:10:24.982
A historical relic. They took
the temple down. piece by piece...

747
01:10:25.187 --> 01:10:30.250
...then put it back together.
How crazy.

748
01:10:35.097 --> 01:10:36.428
Where is it?

749
01:11:10.666 --> 01:11:11.928
Open up.

750
01:11:12.735 --> 01:11:14.794
Open up! Police business!

751
01:11:21.577 --> 01:11:25.638
Christ! How'd they fit
this temple in there?

752
01:11:53.208 --> 01:11:56.905
Which one of you is Lin Tao-sheng?
And Huang Yi-feng?

753
01:12:00.983 --> 01:12:04.384
Lin Tao-sheng. Huang Yi-feng.

754
01:12:09.658 --> 01:12:11.649
You are the people in charge here?

755
01:12:11.894 --> 01:12:14.158
- We don't have anyone in charge.
- Bullshit!

756
01:12:14.396 --> 01:12:16.159
You didn't register for a license?

757
01:12:19.068 --> 01:12:20.626
What are these?

758
01:12:22.137 --> 01:12:23.126
Take them all away.

759
01:12:23.339 --> 01:12:24.431
- Bring them.
- Move it.

760
01:12:24.606 --> 01:12:27.166
- Be cooperative.
- You've violated arms-control laws.

761
01:12:27.409 --> 01:12:29.400
- Hurry!
- Move it!

762
01:12:29.611 --> 01:12:31.078
Take them away!

763
01:12:32.948 --> 01:12:34.677
What is this temple?

764
01:12:35.184 --> 01:12:37.675
- Did you register it?
- What is inside there?

765
01:12:37.986 --> 01:12:39.453
Out of the way.

766
01:13:05.514 --> 01:13:10.042
- Officer down! Help!
- Send backup now!

767
01:13:11.487 --> 01:13:12.419
Hurry up!

768
01:14:17.719 --> 01:14:19.050
Break the lock!

769
01:16:10.599 --> 01:16:13.534
This is Li Yun-chan at the scene
of the massacre...

770
01:16:13.702 --> 01:16:16.364
...that took place inside
the Central World Building.

771
01:16:16.572 --> 01:16:20.406
Nine officers and 24 members
of the True Sage cult...

772
01:16:20.676 --> 01:16:22.405
...are listed as dead.

773
01:16:22.678 --> 01:16:27.945
It has been confirmed that
Huang Yi-feng was killed.

774
01:16:31.019 --> 01:16:33.044
- Among them are professors. doctors...

775
01:16:33.255 --> 01:16:36.588
...police officers
and even politicians.

776
01:16:36.792 --> 01:16:39.727
Acting on new information.
police raided 50...

777
01:17:47.663 --> 01:17:50.826
Officer Huang. the foreigner
inside wants to see you.

778
01:18:05.213 --> 01:18:06.703
What's happened?

779
01:18:07.315 --> 01:18:08.805
I found something.

780
01:18:19.061 --> 01:18:20.392
Come help.

781
01:18:24.900 --> 01:18:25.924
Pull!

782
01:18:35.410 --> 01:18:37.071
What the hell?

783
01:19:08.076 --> 01:19:09.839
She needs an ambulance!

784
01:19:10.746 --> 01:19:11.906
Stretcher!

785
01:19:12.681 --> 01:19:14.410
Emergency! Hurry!

786
01:19:16.084 --> 01:19:18.348
Out of the way!

787
01:19:23.458 --> 01:19:26.188
Agent Richter! Agent Richter!

788
01:19:26.461 --> 01:19:29.988
Can you give your views
on these strange murders?

789
01:19:30.198 --> 01:19:33.827
My personal view's unimportant.
Get your cable off me!

790
01:19:36.605 --> 01:19:39.267
There's talk of supernatural
aspects to these crimes.

791
01:19:39.474 --> 01:19:41.874
That the killer wanted
to attain immortality.

792
01:19:42.077 --> 01:19:43.374
They definitely failed.

793
01:19:43.578 --> 01:19:47.571
But some officers have experienced
supernatural phenomena.

794
01:19:47.783 --> 01:19:49.751
Can you comment on that?

795
01:20:00.195 --> 01:20:02.186
Hey! How is...?

796
01:20:03.532 --> 01:20:05.500
Your captain. how is he?

797
01:20:06.701 --> 01:20:10.262
Got some 30 stitches.
You could even see his ribs.

798
01:20:10.505 --> 01:20:11.904
I'll go see him.

799
01:20:12.407 --> 01:20:16.104
He's under sedation.
The doctors want him to rest.

800
01:20:22.250 --> 01:20:23.740
And the girl?

801
01:20:25.053 --> 01:20:28.921
Her condition isn't critical.
She was already ill anyway.

802
01:20:29.291 --> 01:20:31.225
What do you mean she was ill?

803
01:20:33.995 --> 01:20:37.226
"Hsieh Ya-li.
Benign brain tumor exerts pressure...

804
01:20:37.432 --> 01:20:40.799
...on her pituitary gland
and optic chiasma and expands...

805
01:20:41.069 --> 01:20:45.165
...to both sides of the forehead.
Condition deemed inoperable."

806
01:20:45.607 --> 01:20:47.666
How about the injury
on her belly?

807
01:20:47.876 --> 01:20:52.108
The skin on her belly
had been peeled off...

808
01:20:52.347 --> 01:20:56.579
...and was used to cultivate...
What's it called? A bug-born fungus.

809
01:20:59.554 --> 01:21:02.955
The bureau has notified me
that Lin Tao-sheng...

810
01:21:03.124 --> 01:21:06.423
...has confessed to the murders.

811
01:21:09.965 --> 01:21:11.227
Case closed.

812
01:21:51.606 --> 01:21:54.006
Where do you want to eat?
It's my treat.

813
01:21:54.242 --> 01:21:59.509
No. it's mine. Those noodles of yours
almost killed me last time.

814
01:22:01.349 --> 01:22:03.874
Since it's my last night here...

815
01:22:04.386 --> 01:22:07.048
...I thought we'd do something more
appropriate.

816
01:22:08.356 --> 01:22:10.347
Got some directions here.

817
01:22:11.960 --> 01:22:15.225
Take a left at this next street.
Yeah.

818
01:22:19.034 --> 01:22:20.228
And...?

819
01:22:20.802 --> 01:22:22.429
And then. you...

820
01:22:25.674 --> 01:22:28.302
...take a right
at the next light. I think.

821
01:22:28.576 --> 01:22:30.567
- It's the one after.
- Oh.

822
01:22:31.446 --> 01:22:32.640
Okay.

823
01:22:34.916 --> 01:22:36.508
You take it from here.

824
01:22:43.158 --> 01:22:45.752
Hey. you are late.
Dinner is ready.

825
01:22:45.927 --> 01:22:48.225
- Good. I'm starving.
- Welcome. welcome.

826
01:22:48.463 --> 01:22:49.623
Thank you.

827
01:22:52.233 --> 01:22:54.258
Hi. Welcome home.

828
01:23:03.144 --> 01:23:07.774
So you're not interested in staying
more days as a tourist?

829
01:23:10.051 --> 01:23:12.576
You will remember us only for death.

830
01:23:13.421 --> 01:23:17.551
Actually. the true beauty
of the island is on the East Coast.

831
01:23:17.726 --> 01:23:20.217
Like Su-ao. a little fishing village.

832
01:23:20.462 --> 01:23:22.828
Huang was born there. Very pretty.

833
01:23:22.998 --> 01:23:25.057
Well. it sounds nice.

834
01:23:26.101 --> 01:23:30.504
But to be perfectly honest with you.
I'm a little homesick.

835
01:23:31.139 --> 01:23:34.074
Been a long time.
the job's done and...

836
01:23:36.144 --> 01:23:40.581
Well. you know what? I got a week's
vacation coming at Christmas...

837
01:23:40.782 --> 01:23:42.807
...and maybe you two
will have me back.

838
01:23:44.486 --> 01:23:46.716
- Show me around.
- Sure.

839
01:23:46.888 --> 01:23:48.583
If it's not too cold.

840
01:23:50.392 --> 01:23:52.860
Compared to the States.
we never get too cold.

841
01:23:53.228 --> 01:23:54.559
Then it's a date.

842
01:23:57.365 --> 01:23:59.094
Here's to Huo-tu's wife.

843
01:24:01.436 --> 01:24:02.869
And to Mei-mei.

844
01:24:05.573 --> 01:24:09.031
And this meal
and your gracious hospitality.

845
01:24:10.311 --> 01:24:12.142
And thank your mother.

846
01:24:14.482 --> 01:24:16.109
What's so funny?

847
01:24:16.584 --> 01:24:18.211
Someone tell me what's so funny.

848
01:24:18.420 --> 01:24:19.444
Mei-mei.

849
01:24:23.324 --> 01:24:26.760
- It's my fault.
- Somebody tell me what's so funny.

850
01:24:27.896 --> 01:24:29.659
It's my fault.

851
01:24:31.633 --> 01:24:32.998
Go to sleep.

852
01:24:41.309 --> 01:24:44.904
It'd be a lot easier for us
if there were evil spirits.

853
01:24:46.347 --> 01:24:50.113
Unfortunately. man is worse than
any figment of our imagination.

854
01:24:50.952 --> 01:24:54.444
- You're good.
- I am. aren't I?

855
01:24:55.356 --> 01:24:58.416
I give these things
dozens of times a year.

856
01:24:59.027 --> 01:25:01.928
Now I am just tired.

857
01:25:02.564 --> 01:25:06.523
I'm tired of... Tired of pretending.

858
01:25:08.803 --> 01:25:10.464
Everything is...

859
01:25:11.306 --> 01:25:14.707
Everything is under control.

860
01:25:16.478 --> 01:25:17.968
Until the next...

861
01:25:18.713 --> 01:25:21.113
...atrocity comes along.

862
01:25:23.084 --> 01:25:24.312
And it will.

863
01:25:27.255 --> 01:25:29.450
More and more. I just want to...

864
01:25:30.391 --> 01:25:34.794
I just want to scream. I don't want
to talk. just scream.

865
01:25:44.606 --> 01:25:47.939
You and your wife. why don't you
sleep in the same room?

866
01:25:49.577 --> 01:25:50.669
No.

867
01:25:51.446 --> 01:25:54.006
Mei-mei always gets nightmares.

868
01:25:55.116 --> 01:25:58.677
She feels more comfortable
when her mom's around.

869
01:25:58.887 --> 01:26:00.252
Don't you miss...?

870
01:26:03.291 --> 01:26:05.452
How long has it been since...?

871
01:26:08.596 --> 01:26:12.862
Is there any question too personal
for an American to ask?

872
01:26:13.067 --> 01:26:15.058
Yes. definitely.

873
01:26:16.437 --> 01:26:18.200
- But not me.
- So...

874
01:26:19.307 --> 01:26:22.765
So tell me about your family.
Your wife.

875
01:26:28.149 --> 01:26:30.083
My wife is long gone.

876
01:26:31.419 --> 01:26:34.252
How come you still
wear your wedding ring?

877
01:26:41.329 --> 01:26:42.819
Ready for another one?

878
01:26:43.798 --> 01:26:44.924
- I'll get it.
- I will.

879
01:26:45.099 --> 01:26:46.999
- No. no.
- I'll get it.

880
01:26:49.170 --> 01:26:50.467
Maybe not.

881
01:27:27.709 --> 01:27:28.733
What?

882
01:27:29.711 --> 01:27:31.008
What is it?

883
01:28:07.415 --> 01:28:08.404
Kevin.

884
01:28:09.884 --> 01:28:11.408
Time to get up.

885
01:28:14.422 --> 01:28:15.616
Kevin.

886
01:28:16.724 --> 01:28:18.624
You've got a flight to catch.

887
01:28:58.966 --> 01:29:00.831
What the hell is going on?

888
01:29:01.536 --> 01:29:03.026
Didn't you sleep here
last night?

889
01:29:03.738 --> 01:29:05.899
- Not ask so many questions.

890
01:29:07.008 --> 01:29:09.772
What the hell
are you mumbling about?

891
01:29:11.612 --> 01:29:14.877
Too much. So many questions.

892
01:29:21.089 --> 01:29:22.920
There's mold in his nasal cavity.

893
01:29:23.124 --> 01:29:25.251
Like the victims before him.

894
01:29:26.761 --> 01:29:31.255
It looks like he just
yanked off his own tongue.

895
01:29:34.369 --> 01:29:38.601
How is it possible
that he was harmed. but not you?

896
01:29:54.989 --> 01:29:56.752
Get the doctor. quick!

897
01:29:59.026 --> 01:30:01.324
- What are you saying?
- Mei-mei...

898
01:30:01.562 --> 01:30:03.154
...is talking to me.

899
01:30:04.699 --> 01:30:06.428
Out of the way.

900
01:30:07.402 --> 01:30:09.233
What poison has he taken?

901
01:30:10.304 --> 01:30:13.705
- I don't know.
- Why is there so much serotonin?

902
01:30:14.375 --> 01:30:15.865
Two cc's haloperidol.

903
01:30:16.477 --> 01:30:17.842
IV push.

904
01:30:18.579 --> 01:30:20.513
Tell me. how he is doing?

905
01:30:20.882 --> 01:30:22.782
- What happened?
- Family will wait outside!

906
01:30:23.017 --> 01:30:24.541
Please tell me how he is.

907
01:30:24.786 --> 01:30:27.084
He is probably flying through space.

908
01:30:29.624 --> 01:30:32.718
In Taiwan. less than 24 hours
after being interviewed...

909
01:30:32.894 --> 01:30:37.263
...on the True Sage serial killings.
FBI Agent Kevin Richter...

910
01:30:37.532 --> 01:30:40.433
...has been found murdered
in a Taipei apartment.

911
01:30:40.768 --> 01:30:45.262
He is the latest victim in what was
thought to be a solved case.

912
01:30:45.673 --> 01:30:49.871
Another theory claims he was killed to
complete the fifth path to immortality.

913
01:30:50.211 --> 01:30:53.908
Richter publicly claimed he didn't
believe in spirits or demons.

914
01:30:54.182 --> 01:30:57.913
He was therefore condemned to
the tongue-extracting punishment...

915
01:30:58.186 --> 01:30:59.483
...for the unbeliever.

916
01:30:59.687 --> 01:31:02.451
To understand Richter's death.
one has to go...

917
01:31:04.091 --> 01:31:05.888
- these "Chi" represent
from May to July...

918
01:31:06.060 --> 01:31:08.893
...they also represent
fire. Huo. and earth. Tu.

919
01:31:09.197 --> 01:31:11.529
The murder is quite something.

920
01:31:11.732 --> 01:31:16.066
He must be gravely ill to be able
to distill a potion like this.

921
01:31:16.370 --> 01:31:17.928
Why must he be gravely ill?

922
01:31:18.139 --> 01:31:19.766
According to Taoism...

923
01:31:20.308 --> 01:31:22.708
...grave illness is essential
for attaining immortality.

924
01:31:23.044 --> 01:31:26.980
Only in grave illness can a person
experience real awakening.

925
01:32:25.773 --> 01:32:29.106
Where's that girl? Hsieh Ya-li?

926
01:32:29.777 --> 01:32:31.745
I'm a police officer.

927
01:32:33.548 --> 01:32:36.108
- She's disappeared.
- Disappeared?

928
01:32:36.450 --> 01:32:40.546
Just disappeared.
Since this afternoon.

929
01:32:43.024 --> 01:32:45.458
Aren't you...? Aren't you the guy...?

930
01:32:45.760 --> 01:32:47.557
EMERGENC Y ROOM

931
01:32:50.097 --> 01:32:51.428
Ching Fang.

932
01:32:52.967 --> 01:32:55.333
- Central World Building.
- Are you there?

933
01:32:55.570 --> 01:32:57.265
I don't know what happened.

934
01:32:57.471 --> 01:32:59.234
I am unable to wake up.

935
01:32:59.840 --> 01:33:04.868
The girl who is sick
is coming to see me.

936
01:33:05.179 --> 01:33:08.273
She told me that
she killed everyone.

937
01:33:08.616 --> 01:33:12.882
She hides in the cave
and meditates.

938
01:33:13.521 --> 01:33:16.979
She found me
according to the scriptures.

939
01:33:18.459 --> 01:33:22.054
She also said
all her disciples are gone now.

940
01:33:23.331 --> 01:33:24.662
But she is not afraid.

941
01:33:24.865 --> 01:33:26.890
She can still be immortal.

942
01:33:27.868 --> 01:33:29.768
It will not be an obstacle.

943
01:33:35.409 --> 01:33:36.876
Ching Fang.

944
01:33:38.312 --> 01:33:39.574
Are you there?

945
01:33:41.048 --> 01:33:42.572
Anyone there?

946
01:33:43.851 --> 01:33:45.113
Hello?

947
01:35:57.952 --> 01:35:59.442
Who are you?

948
01:36:00.521 --> 01:36:02.512
What the hell do you want?

949
01:36:03.090 --> 01:36:06.082
Everything has already been destined.

950
01:36:07.061 --> 01:36:09.859
You came to see me off. Come.

951
01:36:11.098 --> 01:36:15.558
To hell with you! I am a police officer.
You are under arrest.

952
01:36:15.803 --> 01:36:19.102
On your knees.
Hands behind your back.

953
01:36:20.107 --> 01:36:24.066
You seem so sad.
Do you need me to help you?

954
01:36:28.716 --> 01:36:32.880
Come. Come back to
the hospital with me.

955
01:36:34.922 --> 01:36:38.824
Really?
Can the hospital help you?

956
01:36:42.830 --> 01:36:45.025
Would you rather have Mei-mei here?

957
01:36:48.402 --> 01:36:51.860
Maybe she can help you.

958
01:36:56.177 --> 01:36:57.542
Daddy!

959
01:36:58.145 --> 01:37:00.579
Yuan! Don't shoot! Yuan!

960
01:37:00.748 --> 01:37:03.114
Your daddy forced me to do this.

961
01:37:04.051 --> 01:37:05.916
- Yuan!
- Daddy!

962
01:37:11.725 --> 01:37:12.953
Huo-tu!

963
01:37:13.627 --> 01:37:17.961
Have you ever really cared about us?
Have you really needed us?

964
01:37:47.494 --> 01:37:50.258
Come on. Shoot me too.

965
01:37:53.701 --> 01:37:54.998
Help me.

966
01:37:56.604 --> 01:38:01.940
I don't believe people
can attain immortality.

967
01:38:04.144 --> 01:38:07.773
I am a police officer.
Foreign Affairs division.

968
01:38:08.883 --> 01:38:12.512
I am arresting you as a suspect...

969
01:38:13.654 --> 01:38:15.349
...of serial murders.

970
01:38:29.570 --> 01:38:31.800
This is not real.

971
01:38:37.211 --> 01:38:38.678
I am...

972
01:38:39.480 --> 01:38:41.971
...Huang Huo-tu.

973
01:38:43.484 --> 01:38:47.045
I neglected the lives
of my wife and daughter.

974
01:38:47.688 --> 01:38:50.680
And ignored the deaths
of my colleagues.

975
01:38:51.058 --> 01:38:54.824
You think I will help you?
Come on.

976
01:38:55.029 --> 01:38:56.257
Come on!

977
01:38:58.065 --> 01:38:59.259
Give it to me!

978
01:38:59.500 --> 01:39:03.766
One shot and your heart
will stop instantly.

979
01:39:04.138 --> 01:39:07.369
Your body will respond as if
you died from a gunshot.

980
01:39:08.475 --> 01:39:12.002
You know when you die.
your wife and Mei-mei...

981
01:39:12.212 --> 01:39:14.305
What will their lives be like?

982
01:39:18.352 --> 01:39:20.149
So pathetic!

983
01:39:20.354 --> 01:39:22.618
With no one to take care of them.

984
01:39:42.843 --> 01:39:45.471
EMERGENC Y ROOM

985
01:39:53.053 --> 01:39:54.077
Huo-tu.

986
01:39:54.555 --> 01:39:56.022
Are you all right?

987
01:39:57.624 --> 01:39:59.421
Where's the girl?

988
01:39:59.626 --> 01:40:01.025
Inside.

989
01:40:01.428 --> 01:40:02.895
Is she badly injured?

990
01:40:04.465 --> 01:40:07.298
The bullet didn't enter.
It grazed her skull.

991
01:40:08.736 --> 01:40:12.900
Did you check her eyes?
Is there anything unusual about them?

992
01:40:13.107 --> 01:40:14.404
Unusual?

993
01:40:14.608 --> 01:40:17.270
Does she have two pupils in one eye?

994
01:40:19.880 --> 01:40:21.108
Come with me.

995
01:40:23.317 --> 01:40:26.411
Seventeen years ago.
her mother gave birth here.

996
01:40:26.620 --> 01:40:30.784
She gave birth to twins.
One was stillborn. She was the other.

997
01:40:30.991 --> 01:40:34.552
She was never a happy child.
No one to care for her.

998
01:40:34.728 --> 01:40:38.892
They found a tumor in her brain.
She claimed she could see things.

999
01:40:39.099 --> 01:40:42.432
You know what I mean?
She said she could see her sister.

1000
01:40:43.170 --> 01:40:48.767
This is not unusual.
Brain-tumor patients react like this.

1001
01:40:49.009 --> 01:40:53.070
It's like they're on drugs.
Like they're possessed.

1002
01:40:53.881 --> 01:40:56.679
It's difficult
to explain scientifically.

1003
01:40:56.884 --> 01:41:02.288
During her stay here. she found out
about her stillborn twin and changed.

1004
01:41:02.523 --> 01:41:05.014
She said her sister was not dead...

1005
01:41:05.726 --> 01:41:10.186
...but had attained immortality.
The double pupils prove this.

1006
01:41:27.581 --> 01:41:29.139
You scared me.

1007
01:41:30.084 --> 01:41:32.985
- Are you all right?
- I am now.

1008
01:41:34.321 --> 01:41:35.447
Where's Mei-mei?

1009
01:41:36.723 --> 01:41:40.318
Sleeping.
I'll wake her up for dinner.

1010
01:41:41.862 --> 01:41:44.353
Sleeping? Is she ill?

1011
01:41:57.945 --> 01:42:00.038
DIVORCE AGREEMENT

1012
01:42:04.284 --> 01:42:06.343
SIGNED AND EXECUTED

1013
01:42:19.867 --> 01:42:25.134
Get up! Think you can
get away with this?

1014
01:42:25.706 --> 01:42:28.197
Can you hear me? Get up!

1015
01:42:28.408 --> 01:42:31.866
- Ching Fang.
- Like father. like daughter!

1016
01:42:32.112 --> 01:42:34.603
I'm telling you to get up!

1017
01:42:37.951 --> 01:42:39.111
Huo-tu.

1018
01:42:40.420 --> 01:42:42.945
I don't know what to do with her.

1019
01:42:43.991 --> 01:42:46.482
Say you're sorry.
Apologize.

1020
01:42:46.727 --> 01:42:48.490
What are you doing?

1021
01:43:43.984 --> 01:43:45.747
I must go.

1022
01:43:47.588 --> 01:43:49.988
You will come with me too.

1023
01:44:06.006 --> 01:44:08.167
It has all been ordained.

1024
01:44:15.549 --> 01:44:17.210
Don't be afraid.

1025
01:44:17.851 --> 01:44:19.250
I'm not afraid.

1026
01:44:21.855 --> 01:44:23.379
Be brave.

1027
01:44:29.529 --> 01:44:31.656
I'm going now.

1028
01:45:13.340 --> 01:45:14.466
Huo-tu!

1029
01:45:16.810 --> 01:45:18.004
Huo-tu!

1030
01:45:19.112 --> 01:45:22.946
I want to review the reports
before they go to your superiors.

1031
01:45:24.251 --> 01:45:27.743
Where's Huo-tu?
Where's Huo-tu?

1032
01:45:30.023 --> 01:45:31.752
That's not him!

1033
01:45:31.958 --> 01:45:34.426
That's the girl.

1034
01:45:48.375 --> 01:45:50.275
He did not suffer.

1035
01:45:59.219 --> 01:46:02.347
We gave him CPR for a long time.
We did our best.

1036
01:46:18.839 --> 01:46:19.965
Wake up.

1037
01:46:23.009 --> 01:46:24.169
Wake up.

1038
01:46:25.445 --> 01:46:28.505
I know you can hear me.

1039
01:46:29.416 --> 01:46:31.247
Wake up. Can you hear me?

1040
01:46:31.718 --> 01:46:33.618
He inhaled too much mold bacteria.

1041
01:46:34.621 --> 01:46:36.316
His heart couldn't take it.

1042
01:46:38.425 --> 01:46:40.825
Wake up. Wake up!

1043
01:46:41.928 --> 01:46:44.419
- Let him go!
- No. I have to try!

1044
01:46:44.998 --> 01:46:47.125
I know he can hear me!

1045
01:46:47.868 --> 01:46:51.463
I will get him back.
I will get him back!

1046
01:46:51.772 --> 01:46:54.104
Come back!

1047
01:46:56.042 --> 01:46:59.978
You can't abandon me and Mei-mei!

1048
01:47:00.180 --> 01:47:02.705
Come back!

1049
01:47:04.851 --> 01:47:06.318
Come back.

1050
01:47:20.066 --> 01:47:23.558
Tell your father to wake up.

1051
01:47:32.813 --> 01:47:35.839
Mommy. Mommy?

1052
01:47:36.616 --> 01:47:38.982
What is Daddy laughing at?

1053
01:47:40.153 --> 01:47:41.484
Daddy loves you...

1054
01:47:41.688 --> 01:47:45.180
...but doesn't know how to tell you.
so all he can do is smile.

1055
01:47:52.599 --> 01:47:54.157
Daddy.

1056
01:47:59.005 --> 01:48:00.472
Daddy.

1057
01:48:15.655 --> 01:48:18.488
Look at his eyes.

1058
01:48:24.498 --> 01:48:25.590
Paramedics!

1059
01:48:27.033 --> 01:48:29.763
Get him to the hospital!

1060
01:48:30.270 --> 01:48:31.794
He's crying!

1061
01:48:58.265 --> 01:49:00.756
LOVE CAUSES SORROW

1062
01:49:01.535 --> 01:49:04.060
LOVE CAUSES FEAR

1063
01:49:04.838 --> 01:49:07.500
THOSE SEPARATED FROM LOVE

1064
01:49:08.241 --> 01:49:11.074
HAVE NO SORROW AND NO FEAR

1065
01:49:11.878 --> 01:49:16.474
FROM A STONE CARVING
EX CAVATED FROM JIAO CHI. CHINA

